OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Mortgage borrowing rules have been     
OL,6, eased after the Bank of England        
OL,7, scrapped an affordability test.        
OL,9,FThe "stress test" forced lenders to    
OL,10,Fcalculate whether potential borrowers  
OL,11,Fwould be able to cope if interest rates
OL,12,Fclimbed by up to 3%.                   
OL,14,FRemoving the test may help some        
OL,15,Fpotential borrowers get loans, such as 
OL,16,Fthe self-employed or freelance workers.
OL,18,FBut other rules such as strict         
OL,19,Floan-to-income limits will not make it 
OL,20,Feasier for most people to get a        
OL,21,Fmortgage.                              
